snippet.title: Wayfinder - Official Reveal Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
►► Join the Closed Beta: http://www.playwayfinder.com

Become a Wayfinder, and unlock their powers as you choose your path and playstyle while pushing back a hostile force that has overtaken your world.

Directly shape and customize the adventures you go on with friends, because Wayfinders are stronger together.

#ps4 #ps5 #ps5games #ps4games
